headline: ConocoPhillips (COP): Valuation Update Following Dividend Hike and Raised Production Guidance
summary: ConocoPhillips (COP) just posted quarterly results that surpassed analyst estimates, due to higher oil and gas production as well as effective cost controls. The company also raised its full-year production guidance and increased its quarterly dividend by 8%. See our latest analysis for ConocoPhillips.
